ef=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Die <strong><code>Number.parseInt()</code></strong> Methode liest ein String-Argument ein und gibt eine ganze Zahl im angegebenen Zahlensystem zurück.</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"490\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/number-parseint.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">Number.parseInt(<var>string</var>[, <var>radix</var>])</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameter","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\"><dl>\n <dt id=\"string\"><code>string</code></dt>\n <dd>Umzuwandelnder Wert. Wenn <code>string</code> kein String ist, wird er zu einem String konvertiert (durch die abstrakte Operation <code><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-tostring\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ToString</a></code>). Führende Leerzeichen im String werden ignoriert.</dd>\n</dl><dl>\n <dt id=\"radix\"><code>radix</code></dt>\n <dd>Eine ganze Zahl zwischen 2 und 36, die die Basis eines mathematischen Zahlensystems ist, in der der String geschrieben ist. 10 steht für das gebräuchliche Dezimalsystem.</dd>\n</dl></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"rückgabewert","title":"Rückgabewert","isH3":true,"content":"<p></p><p>Eine ganze Zahl des übergebenen Strings. Wenn das erste Zeichen nicht zu einer Zahl konvertiert werden kann, wird <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/NaN\"><code>NaN</code></a> zurückgegeben.</p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beschreibung","title":"Beschreibung","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Diese Methode hat den gleichen Funktionsumfang wie die globalen <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/parseInt\"><code>parseInt()</code></a> Funktion:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>Number<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>parseInt <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> parseInt<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Sie ist Teil von ECMAScript 2015 und hat als Ziel die Modularisierung von globalen Funktionen. Mehr Details und Beispiele im Artikel <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/parseInt\"><code>parseInt()</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"polyfill","title":"Polyfill","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Number<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>parseInt <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">undefined</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    Number<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>parseInt <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>parseInt<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Komment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-number.parseint\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Number.parseInt' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initiale Definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-number.parseint\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'Number.parseInt' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Number.parseInt","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number/parseInt/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number\"><code>Number</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/parseInt\"><code>parseInt()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beschreibung","id":"beschreibung"},{"text":"Polyfill","id":"polyfill"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browserkompatibilität","id":"browserkompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Die Number.parseInt() Methode liest ein String-Argument ein und gibt eine ganze Zahl im angegebenen Zahlensystem zurück.","popularity":0,"modified":